{"title":"Update: Customs and Border Patrol Reverses Its Big Bend Border Wall Plans","link":"https://theradavist.com/trump-administration-border-wall-big-bend","date":1772785849000,"content":"<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/02/Big-Bend-Border-Wall-Bike-Camping.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/02/Big-Bend-Border-Wall-Bike-Camping.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/02/Big-Bend-Border-Wall-Bike-Camping.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/02/Big-Bend-Border-Wall-Bike-Camping.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://ourpubliclandsandwaters.substack.com/p/customs-and-border-patrol-reverses?fbclid=\" target=\"_blank\">Our Public Lands and Backwaters</a> is reporting that Customs and Border Patrol has reversed its Border Wall in Bend Bend plans! Now, we’d like to think it’s the hundreds of thousands of emails they received. Or maybe they realized how absurd this idea was. At any rate, we’d like to thank you for remaining diligent as our Public Lands are under attack!</p>\n<p>Old post is below:</p>\n<p><strong>Big Bend Border Wall:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/e/2PACX-1vRQTnyewnrm2U7Sej5IBUfgoQUe9OOdTc6pO2A2HVhW36pY6lcoZGQB5zZ0f0GMpg/pub?utm_source=ig&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_content=link_in_bio&amp;fbclid=PAZXh0bgNhZW0CMTEAc3J0YwZhcHBfaWQMMjU2MjgxMDQwNTU4AAGnvxiaWc1gF9fxM279LsqQbYymxwZPAvkuOh4s6AAazOnOkkPQBOTzKloAjGo_aem_6d-X88f_N2D3RRTfuMRmRw\" target=\"_blank\">Fact sheet. What is happening?</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://5calls.org/state/texas/texas-border-wall-big-bend/?utm_source=ig&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_content=link_in_bio&amp;fbclid=PAZXh0bgNhZW0CMTEAc3J0YwZhcHBfaWQMMjU2MjgxMDQwNTU4AAGnq5grUd1L4mFUi4kSdlRgIMsmlyMqAilZQOCfsKGFjnQEF8Bl2cgDl3YAgik_aem_w6RCc8OrjgEjRZIw_HhJSQ\" target=\"_blank\">Call your elected officials</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.change.org/p/stop-the-construction-of-the-wall-in-big-bend-ranch-state-park-big-bend-national-park?utm_source=ig&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_content=link_in_bio&amp;fbclid=PAZXh0bgNhZW0CMTEAc3J0YwZhcHBfaWQMMjU2MjgxMDQwNTU4AAGnqfHE7xk5fWfFC3F4VYjMv2JkK2ye_ZHV7wIpFN2ofH_IbpUH8RbW2AruI2o_aem_JN-WYNfyTT_YRTkShzzLXw\" target=\"_blank\">Sign the petition</a>.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>One of <span>Texas’s two National Parks, <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/tag/big-bend\" target=\"_blank\">Big Bend</a>, is at risk of losing extensive environmental protections so </span>the Trump Administration can install the Border Wall. This includes Federal Land in Big Bend National Park and State Land in Big Bend State Park, a popular area for <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/big-bend-bike-camping-jolene-holland\" target=\"_blank\">bike camping</a> and <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/chiwawan-wakk-trak-chimichanga-aka-big-bender-desertion-ultra-romance\" target=\"_blank\">mountain biking</a>.</p>\n<p>Marfa Public Radio reports that:</p>\n<blockquote><p><em>“Among the federal regulations to be waived for the project are the National Environmental Policy Act, the Endangered Species Act, the Clean Water Act and a variety of wildlife and historic resources protection laws.”</em></p></blockquote>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/02/Big-Bend-Border-Wall.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/02/Big-Bend-Border-Wall.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/02/Big-Bend-Border-Wall.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://images.theradavist.com/uploads/2026/02/Big-Bend-Border-Wall.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>Similar attacks on Public Land for the Border Wall have taken place in <a href=\"https://www.npca.org/articles/2325-the-border-wall-is-destroying-what-this-park-was-created-to-protect\" target=\"_blank\">Organ Pipe Cactus National Monument</a>, the <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/mining-and-gravel-cycling-patagonia-arizona\" target=\"_blank\">San Rafael Valley outside of Patagonia</a>, Arizona, and countless acres of BLM land.</p>\n<p>Read the full report at <a href=\"https://www.marfapublicradio.org/news/2026-02-13/trump-administration-waiving-environmental-regulations-for-border-walls-in-big-bend-area\" target=\"_blank\">Marfa Public Radio</a> and see more at <a href=\"https://nobigbendborderwall.com/\" target=\"_blank\">No Big Bend Border Wall</a>.</p>\n<p><strong>Big Bend Border Wall:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/e/2PACX-1vRQTnyewnrm2U7Sej5IBUfgoQUe9OOdTc6pO2A2HVhW36pY6lcoZGQB5zZ0f0GMpg/pub?utm_source=ig&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_content=link_in_bio&amp;fbclid=PAZXh0bgNhZW0CMTEAc3J0YwZhcHBfaWQMMjU2MjgxMDQwNTU4AAGnvxiaWc1gF9fxM279LsqQbYymxwZPAvkuOh4s6AAazOnOkkPQBOTzKloAjGo_aem_6d-X88f_N2D3RRTfuMRmRw\" target=\"_blank\">Fact sheet. What is happening?</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://5calls.org/state/texas/texas-border-wall-big-bend/?utm_source=ig&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_content=link_in_bio&amp;fbclid=PAZXh0bgNhZW0CMTEAc3J0YwZhcHBfaWQMMjU2MjgxMDQwNTU4AAGnq5grUd1L4mFUi4kSdlRgIMsmlyMqAilZQOCfsKGFjnQEF8Bl2cgDl3YAgik_aem_w6RCc8OrjgEjRZIw_HhJSQ\" target=\"_blank\">Call your elected officials</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.change.org/p/stop-the-construction-of-the-wall-in-big-bend-ranch-state-park-big-bend-national-park?utm_source=ig&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_content=link_in_bio&amp;fbclid=PAZXh0bgNhZW0CMTEAc3J0YwZhcHBfaWQMMjU2MjgxMDQwNTU4AAGnqfHE7xk5fWfFC3F4VYjMv2JkK2ye_ZHV7wIpFN2ofH_IbpUH8RbW2AruI2o_aem_JN-WYNfyTT_YRTkShzzLXw\" target=\"_blank\">Sign the petition</a>.</li>\n</ul>\n<p> </p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/trump-administration-border-wall-big-bend\">Update: Customs and Border Patrol Reverses Its Big Bend Border Wall Plans</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://cms.theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"John Watson","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"8f4453b411c234b4959a209816f9b91aea1a703af4e1f43611fc5fb0018cc460","category":"Cycling"}